Thief:
Generally good at sneaking around, favouring stealth rather than the direct
attack.
Thief:
  Location: Somewhere in Daggerford.
  Races: All. (Note Daggerford is picky about letting scum into town)
              (You may need to prove how sneaky you are to just join)
  Stats: High Dexterity
  Armour Restrictions: Light armour.
  Weapon restrictions: No two handed weapons

   See Also. Cleric thief. Grimbrand cleric. (Duergar only)
             Wizard Thief (Multi-class).
